nodes.text: George Lucas Down Under is an article covering the first part for the interview with George Lucas and Rick McCallum at the Screen Producers Association of Australia conference, which included hints at the then-in-development status for Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones and Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith. It was published in Star Wars Insider 42, with the second part eventually being released in Star Wars Insider 43.
